<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:23:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>爱因斯坦探测器探测到不适合任何已知类别的神秘 X 射线瞬变</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/einstein-probe-detects-mysterious-x-ray-transient-that-doesnt-fit-any-known-class</link><description>天文学家报告称，爱因斯坦探测器发现了一种不寻常的 X 射线瞬变现象，该现象不适合任何已知类型的宇宙爆炸。介绍其多波长分析的论文发表在该杂志上&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/einstein-probe-detects-mysterious-x-ray-transient-that-doesnt-fit-any-known-class.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/einstein-probe-detects-mysterious-x-ray-transient-that-doesnt-fit-any-known-class</guid></item><item><title>比热水浴缸更热：45°C 突破性冷却 AI 最大机器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/hotter-than-a-hot-tub-the-45c-breakthrough-to-cool-ais-biggest-machines</link><description>在有利的气候条件下，NVIDIA 的 45 度液冷架构可以通过干式冷却器实现无冷却器运行，将设施冷却水消耗量从传统冷却塔系统每年每兆瓦约 260 万加仑减少到接近于零，用水量最多可减少 100%。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hotter-than-a-hot-tub-the-45c-breakthrough-to-cool-ais-biggest-machines.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/hotter-than-a-hot-tub-the-45c-breakthrough-to-cool-ais-biggest-machines</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 隐瞒了什么！ |星舰更新</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/spacex-is-hiding-something-starship-update</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/spacex-is-hiding-something-starship-update</guid></item><item><title>大脑训练游戏为无药物疼痛管理带来新希望</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-brain-training-game-offers-new-hope-for-drug-free-pain-management</link><description>耳机将玩家的大脑活动数据传输到应用程序，应用程序通过改变水母周围水的颜色来做出响应，为玩家提供有关其精神状态的实时反馈。图片：埃尔瓦·达内尔&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-brain-training-game-offers-new-hope-for-drug-free-pain-management2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-brain-training-game-offers-new-hope-for-drug-free-pain-management</guid></item><item><title>阴天条件下信鸽导航依靠超顺磁性巨噬细胞</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/homing-pigeon-navigation-relies-on-superparamagnetic-macrophages-under-overcast-conditions</link><description>鸟类使用各种导航策略，包括地磁场，尤其是在没有其他线索的情况下，例如在阴天或夜间条件下。喙中的磁铁矿颗粒、眼睛中的隐花色素、细胞离子通道的改变和前庭系统的变化都被提出来解释磁感受，但确切的机制仍然存在争议。在这里，我们使用物理、形态、功能和基因组分析来鉴定肝脏中超顺磁性巨噬细胞的存在。我们发现巨噬细胞耗尽后，在阴天飞行的鸽子缺乏通常的定向能力。当太阳可见时，没有巨噬细胞的鸟类的定向能力没有受到影响，这表明这是它们的主要线索。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/homing-pigeon-navigation-relies-on-superparamagnetic-macrophages-under-overcast-conditions2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/homing-pigeon-navigation-relies-on-superparamagnetic-macrophages-under-overcast-conditions</guid></item><item><title>鼠标移动解锁真实的 AI 视频控制，无需额外的计算成本</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/mouse-moves-unlock-realistic-ai-video-control-with-no-extra-computing-cost</link><description>以色列理工学院开发的一项技术使普通用户能够直观地创建逼真的视频剪辑，而不需要大量的计算资源。被称为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mouse-moves-unlock-realistic-ai-video-control-with-no-extra-computing-cost3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/mouse-moves-unlock-realistic-ai-video-control-with-no-extra-computing-cost</guid></item><item><title>向人工智能提供数据以加速药物发现</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/feeding-data-to-ai-to-speed-up-drug-discovery</link><description>开发新药可能需要进行数千次化学实验才能确定安全、有效且价格合理的药物的正确配方。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/feeding-data-to-ai-to-speed-up-drug-discovery.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/feeding-data-to-ai-to-speed-up-drug-discovery</guid></item><item><title>弦理论可以在不附加任何弦的情况下解释吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/can-string-theory-be-explained-with-no-strings-attached</link><description>研究人员使用“引导”方法表明，一小部分假设可能自然地导致对某些高能过程的弦理论描述。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-string-theory-be-explained-with-no-strings-attached2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/can-string-theory-be-explained-with-no-strings-attached</guid></item><item><title>戈薇金属中破缺的时间反转对称相可能为超导奠定了条件</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/broken-time-reversal-symmetry-phase-in-kagome-metals-may-establish-conditions-for-superconductivity</link><description>物理学家长期以来一直怀疑一种特殊的量子态潜伏在一类被称为戈薇金属的材料中，但证明其存在一直难以实现。现在，韩国科学技术院的 Yeongkwan Kim 领导的团队对戈薇金属进行了实验，为这种奇异状态提供了迄今为止最有力的证据。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/broken-time-reversal-symmetry-phase-in-kagome-metals-may-establish-conditions-for-superconductivity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/broken-time-reversal-symmetry-phase-in-kagome-metals-may-establish-conditions-for-superconductivity</guid></item><item><title>实验颠覆了电子在热致密物质中实际行为的信念</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/experiment-upends-beliefs-on-how-electrons-actually-behave-in-warm-dense-matter</link><description>欧洲 XFEL、亥姆霍兹德累斯顿罗森多夫中心 (HZDR)、罗斯托克大学和其他合作机构的研究人员利用高精度实验证明，最广泛使用的热致密物质中电子行为模型是不准确的。温暖的致密物质的研究具有挑战性，但对于行星内部调查、材料科学和激光聚变实验等众多研究也至关重要。该研究是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/experiment-upends-beliefs-on-how-electrons-actually-behave-in-warm-dense-matter.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/experiment-upends-beliefs-on-how-electrons-actually-behave-in-warm-dense-matter</guid></item></channel></rss>